Portugal Attorney General to Investigate Madeira Debt, Lusa Says

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-09-21T15:36:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/portugal-attorney-general-to-investigate-madeira-debt-lusa-says.html
The Portuguese Attorney General’s
Office will investigate debts that weren’t reported earlier by
the island region of Madeira, news agency Lusa reported, citing
Attorney General Fernando Pinto Monteiro.  The decision was taken following a meeting yesterday with
an official at  Portugal ’s Accounting Tribunal, according to
Lusa.  No-one was immediately available to comment at the office
of the Presidency of the Regional Government of Madeira.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Joao Lima in Lisbon at 
 jlima1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anabela Reis at 
 areis1@bloomberg.net  